{
  "stem": "17515.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 162.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it was-- for a couple days, it was disorganized.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The SS don't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So these were 1,000 people now, in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After, when the Birkenau build it, they come equal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mostly transport from Europe come to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was very famous, two crematorium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not-- maybe couple-- couple days or couple-- couple weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, now there was each number, 3/4 needle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they press it through the skin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You can hear when the-- when the skin was like, pop, pops.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So many Russian soldier, prisoner been also tattooed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "22, 54, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "German too, I will never forget it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I were what the German call.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[GERMAN], what's your name?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Number?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, there was three-- three or four barrack where-- that-- that was in the fall, in-- in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They closed down-- in the evening, barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I believe that was wintertime, because the frosty ground, in the snow on the ground, we have to take bath.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that-- this barrel was deep in the ground.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the time I had big-- almost like I could see my bone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have to jump into the-- into the-- the barrel and wash myself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so the barracks was closed and nobody-- and nobody go into the barracks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the morning, half of those people been froze dead.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You survived it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What was-- do you have-- did you have a number of the barrack in-- in Birkenau?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Do you remember?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- really, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was not by number.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe that we been together with the Polish-Jewish, you know, Polish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Russian soldiers at war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's especially Russian-- Russian soldiers had number with the Polish people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe at start of the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
